有同胞塑造生命的摇篮。","id":16,"figure":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":17},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"负责拷问的教徒","text":"“溟痕”......只不过是遥远的数千数万海里外的“祂”随波而来的些许意志。哪怕只有一丁点，也确确实实在蚕食陆地。","id":18,"figure":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":19},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"负责拷问的教徒","text":"溟痕会将陆地化为另一种海洋。","id":20,"figure":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","id":21},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"......是啊。","id":22,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","id":23},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"伊比利亚是你们计划的第一个牺牲品，格兰法洛也是。","id":24,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_450_1#5$1","id":25},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"极境","text":"......！","id":26,"figure":"avg_npc_450_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":27},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"负责拷问的教徒","text":"......牺牲品？你是不是，用错了词？","id":28,"figure":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","id":29},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"没有。","id":30,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","id":31},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"审判庭会夺走这座小镇，看看这些“美丽”的溟痕，它们一样会。","id":32,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","id":33},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"这里不再是我们的家。不再与那段如火的岁月有瓜葛。","id":34,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1","id":35},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"负责拷问的教徒","text":"蒂亚戈，你不该——","id":36,"figure":"avg_npc_453_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1","id":37},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"乔迪也被带走了......那些逃走的人此刻应该都被惩戒军抓起来了吧。","id":38,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_451_1#7$1","id":39},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蒂亚戈","text":"你们都是凶手。","id":40,"figure":"avg_npc_451_1#7$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":41},{"type":"character","id":42},{"type":"C